# Sprint 16a: exclude internal/historical docs from the fresh public archive.
# git archive PRUNES export-ignored directories wholesale, so we exclude leaf
# paths (subdirs with nothing to keep, plus individual files) rather than the
# whole docs/ tree — that keeps docs/release-notes/v1.0.0.md (the launch note,
# read by release.yml) in the public archive.
docs/adr/** export-ignore
docs/sprints/** export-ignore
docs/architecture.md export-ignore
docs/bugs.md export-ignore
docs/javalens_feeback_from_cursor.md export-ignore
docs/refactoring-tool-contract.md export-ignore
docs/upgrade-checklist.md export-ignore
docs/upstream-parity-v1.4.2.md export-ignore
npm/** export-ignore
CHANGELOG.md export-ignore
